%H A397686 Ridouane Oudra, <a href="/A397686/b397686.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000</a>
%F A397686 a(n) = tau(n^2)*tau_3(n), where tau_3 = A007425.
%F A397686 a(n) = Sum_{d|n} A359037(d).
%F A397686 a(n) = Sum_{d|n} tau(d^6)*tau(n/d).
%F A397686 a(n) = Sum_{d|n} 5^g(d)*tau(n/d)^2, where g(n) = A162642(n).
